    "title": "Lead Revenue Manager at Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd",
    "description": "Grow your career with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Revenue Manager for our Vadodara team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nZomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
